     "prosody/rhyme-of — (prosody/rhyme-of \"cat\") -> list       — words that rhyme"
     "prosody/scansion — (prosody/scansion line) -> stress-pattern (\"u/u/u/u/u/\")"
     "prosody/foot — (prosody/foot pattern) -> foot-name          — 'iambic 'trochaic etc."
     "prosody/meter — (prosody/meter line) -> record{foot count}   — 'iambic-pentameter"
